OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1777551071
OL,3,CInspectorate warns failures at fire
OL,4,Cservice 'raise concerns' about public
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,FA North East fire service has been
OL,8,Ftold to take urgent action after
OL,9,Ffailures were uncovered by the
OL,10,Fsector's inspectorate.
OL,12,FHis Majesty's Inspectorate of
OL,13,FConstabulary and Fire and Rescue
OL,14,FServices has issued an "accelerated
OL,15,Fcause of concern" following an
OL,16,Finspection of Northumberland Fire and
OL,17,FRescue Service.
OL,26,@vD@XOUwD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1777551071
OL,3,CInspectorate warns failures at fire
OL,4,Cservice 'raise concerns' about public
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,FThese are issued when "a fire
OL,8,Fservice's failures raise concerns
OL,9,Fabout public safety". The inspectorate
OL,10,Fsaid this was the case with
OL,11,FNorthumberland Fire and Rescue, the
OL,12,FLocal Democracy Reporting Service
OL,13,Freports.
OL,15,FIt is another blow for the fire
OL,16,Fservice after a troubled year in 2025
OL,17,Fwhich saw the chief and deputy leave
OL,18,Ftheir posts after a damning report
OL,19,Fidentified a "culture of fear" at the
OL,20,Forganisation.
OL,26,@oD@WOUqD@TO]{D@NOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1777551071
OL,3,CInspectorate warns failures at fire
OL,4,Cservice 'raise concerns' about public
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,FThe inspectorate found that NFRS does
OL,8,Fnot "effectively gather and record
OL,9,Fsite-specific risk information (SSRI)
OL,10,Fto protect firefighters and the
OL,11,Fpublic".
OL,13,FSSRI is detailed, pre-planned data for
OL,14,Fhigh-risk premises which is used to
OL,15,Finform firefighter tactics and is
OL,16,Fvital for helping protect
OL,17,Ffirefighters, the public and property
OL,18,Fduring an emergency.
OL,26,@pD@EOUsD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1777551071
OL,3,CInspectorate warns failures at fire
OL,4,Cservice 'raise concerns' about public
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,FExamples were found of risk
OL,8,Finformation "that weren't effective,
OL,9,Faccurate or up to date". Furthermore,
OL,10,Fthe service was found not to have
OL,11,Fgiven staff the "appropriate support"
OL,12,Fto collect risk information.
OL,26,@pD@MOUqD@WO]sD@QOUsD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1777551071
OL,3,CInspectorate warns failures at fire
OL,4,Cservice 'raise concerns' about public
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,FHis Majesty's Chief Inspector of Fire
OL,8,Fand Rescue Services Michelle Skeer
OL,9,Fsaid: "I have issued an accelerated
OL,10,Fcause of concern as Northumberland
OL,11,FFire and Rescue Service doesn't
OL,12,Feffectively manage risk information
OL,13,Ffor high-risk premises. This is vital
OL,14,Ffor helping protect firefighters and
OL,15,Fthe public during an emergency.
OL,26,@qD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1777551071
OL,3,CInspectorate warns failures at fire
OL,4,Cservice 'raise concerns' about public
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,F"During our inspection, we found out-
OL,8,Fof-date risk information, cases where
OL,9,Frisks had been graded inaccurately and
OL,10,Fseveral sites with potential risks
OL,11,Fwhere no site-specific risk
OL,12,Finformation was available.
OL,14,F"The service had identified 478 sites
OL,15,Fas requiring a SSRI record, but its
OL,16,Fquality assurance panel had only
OL,17,Freviewed 37 of these sites. This means
OL,18,Fthe service can't know if its risk
OL,19,Finformation is accurate and I am not
OL,20,Fconfident the service has identified
OL,21,Fall places of risk.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1777551071
OL,3,CInspectorate warns failures at fire
OL,4,Cservice 'raise concerns' about public
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,F"Northumberland Fire and Rescue
OL,8,FService must act urgently to identify
OL,9,Fall sites requiring a risk visit, make
OL,10,Fsure information is accurate and kept
OL,11,Fup to date and give staff the training
OL,12,Fthey need to do this effectively. I
OL,13,Fwill be closely monitoring its
OL,14,Fprogress."
OL,16,FTo address these concerns, HMICFRS has
OL,17,Frecommended that the service should
OL,18,Fmake sure:
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
