PN,42408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1777551071
OL,3,CInspectorate warns failures at fire
OL,4,Cservice 'raise concerns' about public
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FThe improvements will be overseen by
OL,13,FNFRS's new chief, Keith Carruthers `
OL,14,Fwho has only been in post for a matter
OL,15,Fof weeks.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1777551071
OL,3,CInspectorate warns failures at fire
OL,4,Cservice 'raise concerns' about public
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,FResponding to the inspectorate's
OL,8,Ffindings, Mr Carruthers said: "We are
OL,9,Fgrateful to HMICFRS for their thorough
OL,10,Finspection and identifying the need
OL,11,Ffor Northumberland Fire and Rescue
OL,12,Fservice to review its site-specific
OL,13,Frisk information.
OL,15,F"We are developing an action plan
OL,16,Fwhich will ensure all sites are
OL,17,Freviewed appropriately and will
OL,18,Frespond to HMICFRS recommendations in
OL,19,Fline with their timeline.
OL,26,@pD@_OUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1777551071
OL,3,CInspectorate warns failures at fire
OL,4,Cservice 'raise concerns' about public
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,F"Alongside these initial findings and
OL,8,Frecommendations, the outputs from the
OL,9,Ffull inspection, which will be
OL,10,Favailable in the coming months, will
OL,11,Fprovide an opportunity for me as the
OL,12,Fnewly appointed Chief Fire Officer to
OL,13,Ftake stock, and plan for the future of
OL,14,Fthe service.
OL,16,F"I want to take this opportunity to
OL,17,Freassure residents and businesses that
OL,18,Fwe are taking these findings seriously
OL,19,Fand that their safety is at the
OL,20,Fforefront of all we do ` making
OL,21,FNorthumberland safer."
OL,26,@xD@AOU}D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/11
